MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property ArabicNormalization As TokenFilterName

Docs.summary: A token filter that applies the Arabic normalizer to normalize the orthography. See http://lucene.apache.org/core/4_10_3/analyzers-common/org/apache/lucene/analysis/ar/ArabicNormalizationFilter.html.

MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property AsciiFolding As TokenFilterName

MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property CjkBigram As TokenFilterName

MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property CjkWidth As TokenFilterName

MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property Classic As TokenFilterName

MemberSignature.Value: Public Shared ReadOnly Property EdgeNGram As TokenFilterName

Docs.summary: Generates n-grams of the given size(s) starting from the front or the back of an input token. See http://lucene.apache.org/core/4_10_3/analyzers-common/org/apache/lucene/analysis/ngram/EdgeNGramTokenFilter.html.

Docs.summary: Removes elisions. For example, "l'avion" (the plane) will be converted to "avion" (plane). See http://lucene.apache.org/core/4_10_3/analyzers-common/org/apache/lucene/analysis/util/ElisionFilter.html.
